Having trouble viewing the video above? Click here for an alternative viewing platform.Editor's note: The livestream abruptly ended due to technical difficulties.DURBAN - Retired Durban High Court Judge Thumba Pillay will speak at the Victoria and Griffiths Mxenge Memorial Lecture on Thursday evening at the UKZN's Howard College. The annual gathering honours the important roles the Mxenge's played in the struggle to liberate South Africans from apartheid.Griffiths Mxenge, a lawyer and his wife Victoria, were brutally murdered by the apartheid security police in 1981 and 1985 respectively.eNCA